Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}{\pos(100,340)}{\fad(250,500)}{\an8}巨物...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要解雇嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你們...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要衝水了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不用你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要解雇嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(我總覺得好像不能回復正常的生活了)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油～加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(如我所說,平常會在進餐後跑步嗎?)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要解雇嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流汗真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手指還是太放鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真的需要嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:06:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...跪下很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請認真的去做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從清明節之後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得女傭們好像充滿幹勁似的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗耶爾也...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裏做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預定的時間已經過了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放馬過來!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太鬆懈了,要更加地鼓起幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還未行!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}{\pos(430,240)}{\fad(250,500)}{\an8}東西...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人,太郎大人...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然讓太郎大人變得這麼疲憊不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我沒資格來當女傭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗耶爾,別這樣自責自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.72,0:09:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗耶爾也是,女傭隊的大家也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我著想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣就洩氣的我才不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是溫習的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為太郎大人你在上課時經常打瞌睡\N\N所以成績不太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓你由尾趕上的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何我會瞌睡,給我去想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,競然在我說完就睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛..剛才的是什麼呀...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若打瞌睡便會立即放電
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的名字是『學習君』
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣追不上的學習就可以...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適可而止...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天辛苦了你一整天了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人...你...沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不打擾你了,請慢慢休息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.91,0:11:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漫長的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就來開門了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:12:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人! 來玩吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和太郎大人玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在工作以外的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩玩可以嗎? 一點點吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩什麼好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視遊戲?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.72,0:12:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Daihinmi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.72,0:12:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs24}注: Daihinmi : 一種遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yaki ken
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs24}注: Yaki = 夜晚的空氣,Ken = 天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人真好色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人,心情高漲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第11話『突然的求婚』
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回也要好好的聽主人差遣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人,有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身穿長髮婚紗的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個充滿幹勁和活潑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在這裏出現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花右京女傭隊
